<paragraph id="IFRS05_BC8"><paranum>BC8</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 5"/><data name="paranum" value="BC8"/></prolog><body><variant base="SL19780650" id="IFRS05_BC8_V2"> <p id="IFRS05_P0697">In ED 4, the Board proposed that the IFRS should apply to all non&#x2011;current assets except: </p> <ol base="SL19780651" id="IFRS05_L0031" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="SL19780653" id="IFRS05_P0698">goodwill,</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="SL19780655" id="IFRS05_P0699">financial instruments within the scope of <xref base="F19780656" href="../ias39/IAS39_TOC.dita#IAS39_TOC0001" id="IFRS05_X0387">IAS 39 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Financial Instruments: Recognition and Measurement</ph></ph></xref>,<xref keyref="footnotes/IFRS05_FN0023" type="fn"/></p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p base="SL19780660" id="IFRS05_P0700">financial assets under leases, and</p></li><li><li_value>(d)</li_value> <p base="SL19780662" id="IFRS05_P0701">deferred tax assets and assets arising from employee benefits.</p></li></ol></variant></body></paragraph>